detail: MathDQN在DNS的基础上引入了深度强化学习机制，提升了求解算术问题的能力。
evidence: MathDQN models the tree construction as Markov Decision Process and leverage the strengths of deep Q-network (DQN).

detail: DNS使用ALG514数据集进行实验评估。
evidence: The reported accuracy of seq2seq model is only 16.1% in ALG514.

detail: MathDQN使用Dolphin18K数据集进行实验评估。
evidence: CASS further improved the accuracy on Dolphin18K to 29%

detail: FG-Expression通过细粒度表达式解析改进了MathDQN的性能。
evidence: FG-Expression parses an equation template into fine-grained units, called template fragment.

detail: Dolphin18K扩展了MAWPS数据集，增加了更多样化的问题。
evidence: Dolphin18K is another large-scale dataset which contains Chinese math word problems.

detail: MathDQN使用MAWPS数据集进行实验评估。
evidence: We implemented our own version of DNS and evaluated its performance on the large dataset.
